And the only one who can lead them there is the monster that shares Elspeth''s head. The Nightmare. And he''s not eager to share any longer.', 'In a kingdom cursed by dark magic, Elspeth, possessed by a sly Nightmare, teams up with Ravyn to find the final enchanted card and break the curse before the solstice.', 2023, '0356528766', '9780356528762', 430, NULL, 852, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/14431577-L.jpg', '/works/OL35780604W', NULL, '2025', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'two-twisted-crowns-rachel-gillig', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 'public', '2026-03-16 21:36:46', '2026-03-23 04:19:40');
